bgDescription: A small, compact proportioning data card, the data of which is read by the Synthesizer to gain access to Synthesis' corresponding products.
description: Allows the selected Resonators in the team to regain 20 Resonance Energy when they successfully Dodge an attack within 60s. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
